      <title>欧洲银行面临重大贸易冲击抵御能力的考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/european-banks-face-test-of-resilience-to-major-trade-shocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲银行将接受考验，看它们是否有能力抵御全球贸易分裂带来的影响，表现不佳的银行可能会面临股东分红的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/european-banks-face-test-of-resilience-to-major-trade-shocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布鲁克菲尔德房地产投资信托基金连续第二次亏损，称市场正在好转</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/brookfield-reit-posts-second-straight-loss-says-market-is-improving</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克菲尔德资产管理有限公司 (Brookfield Asset Management Ltd.) 为富人打造的房地产基金连续第二年出现亏损，但今年年底的业绩表现较为强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/brookfield-reit-posts-second-straight-loss-says-market-is-improving</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 15:55:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长武伊契奇认为价格风险已平衡，市场押注合理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/ecb-s-vujcic-sees-price-risks-balanced-market-bets-reasonable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员鲍里斯·武伊契奇表示，目前通胀风险处于平衡状态，投资者对利率走向的看法合理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/ecb-s-vujcic-sees-price-risks-balanced-market-bets-reasonable</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 15:27:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Axis Bank 首席执行官表示，印度储备银行将“慢慢来”捍卫卢比</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/usd-inr-rbi-to-play-it-slow-on-defending-rupee-axis-bank-ceo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Axis Bank Ltd. 首席执行官表示，尽管卢比大幅贬值，但印度央行不太可能对卢比采取强有力的捍卫措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/usd-inr-rbi-to-play-it-slow-on-defending-rupee-axis-bank-ceo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 15:22:23 GMT</pubDate>
