    <item>
      <title>制裁后俄罗斯重要港口油轮积压增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/oil-tankers-backlog-grows-at-vital-russian-port-after-sanctions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯主要石油港口科兹米诺附近的油轮积压情况日益严重，这是美国全面制裁对俄罗斯出口造成破坏的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/oil-tankers-backlog-grows-at-vital-russian-port-after-sanctions</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 15:13:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡扎哈集团首席执行官：完成 MAHB 交易只是“时间问题”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-20/completing-mahb-deal-a-matter-of-time-khazahah-chief-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚主权财富基金 Khazanah Nasional Bhd. 认为，该国最大机场运营商马来西亚机场控股有限公司的私有化在多次推迟后完成只是“时间问题”，董事总经理 Amirul Feisal Wan Zahir 在瑞士达沃斯世界经济论坛年会上接受采访时表示。他还讨论了即将上任的美国政府、加密货币和人工智能。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-20/completing-mahb-deal-a-matter-of-time-khazahah-chief-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 15:05:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税减免推动新兴市场货币上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/emerging-stocks-trade-at-biggest-ever-inauguration-day-discount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称唐纳德·特朗普将在其就任美国总统的第一天避免征收新关税，此后，追踪新兴市场货币的指标上涨，而美元大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/emerging-stocks-trade-at-biggest-ever-inauguration-day-discount</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 10:36:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桑切斯罢免首席执行官后，西班牙电信公司领跌西班牙</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/telefonica-leads-losses-in-spain-after-sanchez-pushes-ceo-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙社会党政府出人意料地赶走了该运营商的长期高管，导致西班牙电信公司 (Telefonica SA) 的股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/telefonica-leads-losses-in-spain-after-sanchez-pushes-ceo-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 09:13:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普就职典礼前夕交易清淡，美元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/dollar-slips-in-thin-trading-hours-before-trump-s-inauguration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当天晚些时候有报道称，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普将不会在就职后立即实施激进的关税，美元因此大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/dollar-slips-in-thin-trading-hours-before-trump-s-inauguration</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 05:34:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国期货因关税减免而上涨，美元下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/asian-stocks-to-gain-as-trump-and-xi-discuss-trade-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普上任第一天将暂缓对中国征收特定关税，这令市场松了一口气，推动美国股指期货周一走高。美元下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-19/asian-stocks-to-gain-as-trump-and-xi-discuss-trade-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jan 2025 22:42:19 GMT</pubDate>
